00:10:20.589 --> 00:10:22.089 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:22.123 --> 00:10:23.257 position:35% line:89% align:start
Takemichi?

00:10:23.290 --> 00:10:24.792 position:13% line:89% align:start
You guys, it's really him!

00:10:24.825 --> 00:10:26.293 position:16% line:89% align:start
Valhalla's Number Three!

00:10:27.495 --> 00:10:31.465 position:24% line:5% align:start
-Kazutora Hanemiya!
-(tense music)

00:10:31.499 --> 00:10:33.801 position:35% line:89% align:start
(all gasp)

00:10:33.834 --> 00:10:35.636 position:19% line:89% align:start
(laughs) Hey, awesome!

00:10:35.669 --> 00:10:36.804 position:33% line:89% align:start
I found you!

00:10:36.837 --> 00:10:38.706 position:19% line:83% align:start
I can't believe there's
a kid at my school

00:10:38.739 --> 00:10:39.974 position:21% line:89% align:start
who belongs to Toman.

00:10:40.007 --> 00:10:42.376 position:19% line:83% align:start
-'Kay, now, Takemichi-
-Huh?

00:10:42.409 --> 00:10:44.546 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm taking you to
Valhalla's base.

00:10:44.579 --> 00:10:46.247 position:35% line:89% align:start
Huh? What?!

00:10:46.280 --> 00:10:48.082 position:16% line:89% align:start
Boys! I found Takemichi!

00:10:48.550 --> 00:10:49.817 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:49.850 --> 00:10:52.521 position:27% line:83% align:start
-So this is him?
-Yup.

00:10:52.554 --> 00:10:54.855 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] Um, are
these guys with you?

00:10:54.889 --> 00:10:55.856 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yep.

00:10:55.890 --> 00:10:57.758 position:21% line:83% align:start
These two are my most
trusted lieutenants.

00:10:58.926 --> 00:11:01.162 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] Uh, but
what happened to them?

00:11:01.195 --> 00:11:02.930 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're both walking
with crutches.

00:11:04.098 --> 00:11:06.200 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh, I broke their
legs yesterday.

00:11:06.233 --> 00:11:07.502 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:07.536 --> 00:11:10.171 position:7% line:83% align:start
Why would you break the legs
of your own most-trusted guys?

00:11:10.204 --> 00:11:11.640 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Kazutora] Hmm.

00:11:11.672 --> 00:11:13.774 position:19% line:83% align:start
You got a problem with
what the boss does?

00:11:13.807 --> 00:11:16.277 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Uh, no.
-Good.

00:11:16.310 --> 00:11:18.679 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] How can these
two be so calm and obedient

00:11:18.712 --> 00:11:21.382 position:16% line:83% align:start
when he's literally just
broken both their legs?

00:11:21.415 --> 00:11:22.683 position:16% line:89% align:start
