00:11:22.716 --> 00:11:24.318 position:24% line:89% align:start
He must be insane!

00:11:24.351 --> 00:11:26.220 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hey, hurry up there, Takemichi!

00:11:26.253 --> 00:11:28.455 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] I can't
believe I'm with Kazutora,

00:11:28.489 --> 00:11:29.924 position:16% line:89% align:start
Valhalla's Number Three!

00:11:29.957 --> 00:11:33.027 position:7% line:83% align:start
