00:11:37.566 --> 00:11:39.700 position:7% line:89% align:start
You got nothing to worry about.

00:11:39.733 --> 00:11:40.935 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Everyone?

00:11:40.968 --> 00:11:43.237 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wait, then this could
be the chance I needed

00:11:43.270 --> 00:11:44.305 position:27% line:89% align:start
to talk to Baji.

00:11:45.574 --> 00:11:48.075 position:24% line:83% align:start
But still, this is
some scary shit.

00:11:49.476 --> 00:11:52.479 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Takemichi exhales)

00:11:54.315 --> 00:11:56.951 position:21% line:89% align:start
(students chattering)

00:11:56.984 --> 00:11:59.420 position:16% line:83% align:start
Wow, I'm so glad school's
finally over today.

00:11:59.453 --> 00:12:01.288 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Aren't you?
-Yeah, totally!

00:12:01.322 --> 00:12:02.089 position:27% line:89% align:start
Where do you feel

00:12:02.122 --> 00:12:03.558 position:24% line:83% align:start
