00:12:24.044 --> 00:12:27.081 position:19% line:83% align:start
If I can just get Baji
to come back to Toman,

00:12:27.114 --> 00:12:29.216 position:10% line:89% align:start
then he'll get rid of Kisaki.

00:12:29.250 --> 00:12:32.886 position:10% line:83% align:start
And if Kisaki's out of Toman,
then the future will change.

00:12:34.955 --> 00:12:37.958 position:19% line:83% align:start
I am not gonna let that
future happen again.

00:12:39.460 --> 00:12:40.794 position:35% line:89% align:start
Just watch!

00:12:40.828 --> 00:12:41.996 position:27% line:89% align:start
You'll see, Hina!

00:12:47.368 --> 00:12:49.169 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:12:49.203 --> 00:12:51.372 position:33% line:89% align:start
(all exhale)

00:12:54.975 --> 00:12:58.379 position:16% line:89% align:start
(pedestrians chattering)

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:01.348 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Delinquent] Who gave you
permission to breathe,

00:13:01.382 --> 00:13:02.783 position:16% line:89% align:start
you little piece of shit?

00:13:02.816 --> 00:13:05.520 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, uh, Hanemiya, sir?

00:13:05.553 --> 00:13:06.521 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:13:06.554 --> 00:13:08.556 position:19% line:89% align:start
Just call me Kazutora.

00:13:08.590 --> 00:13:10.924 position:30% line:89% align:start
Okay, well, um,

00:13:10.958 --> 00:13:13.728 position:19% line:83% align:start
at our school, you're a
third-year now, right?

00:13:13.762 --> 00:13:15.229 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Kazutora] Yes.

00:13:15.262 --> 00:13:18.465 position:13% line:83% align:start
It just seems like it would
be a lot more widely known

00:13:18.499 --> 00:13:21.902 position:16% line:83% align:start
that our school had a
student as famous as you.

00:13:21.935 --> 00:13:23.804 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Kazutora] Well, I
only went to school

00:13:23.837 --> 00:13:25.740 position:21% line:83% align:start
the first term of
my first year there.

00:13:25.774 --> 00:13:27.509 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:27.542 --> 00:13:29.143 position:13% line:89% align:start
After that, I was in juvie.

00:13:29.176 --> 00:13:30.177 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:13:30.844 --> 00:13:33.581 position:24% line:89% align:start
(Kazutora chuckles)

00:13:33.615 --> 00:13:34.982 position:27% line:89% align:start
You got arrested?

00:13:36.016 --> 00:13:37.851 position:16% line:89% align:start
What was that all about?

00:13:38.952 --> 00:13:40.888 position:16% line:89% align:start
That was because of him.

00:13:42.356 --> 00:13:44.358 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're almost to our
headquarters now.

00:13:44.391 --> 00:13:45.560 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Takemichi] Him?

00:13:45.593 --> 00:13:47.361 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who's he talking about?

00:13:47.394 --> 00:13:49.798 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, first, I need to
worry about getting Baji out

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:52.066 position:24% line:83% align:start
without all of
Valhalla noticing.

00:13:52.099 --> 00:13:52.900 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:13:55.737 --> 00:13:57.838 position:27% line:89% align:start
Huh? This is it?

00:13:57.871 --> 00:14:00.207 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Yup.
-An arcade?

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:02.042 position:24% line:83% align:start
It went out of
business years ago.

00:14:06.614 --> 00:14:09.316 position:13% line:89% align:start
(gasps) The Headless Angel!

00:14:16.190 --> 00:14:17.525 position:33% line:89% align:start
(doors thud)

00:14:17.559 --> 00:14:20.394 position:21% line:89% align:start
(members chattering)

00:14:28.570 --> 00:14:32.873 position:13% line:83% align:start
